know you're there.

276
00:23:02,798 --> 00:23:04,466
Thanks.

277
00:23:12,641 --> 00:23:14,184
What happened to your leg?

278
00:23:17,604 --> 00:23:18,844
I was trying to make it better.

279
00:23:19,147 --> 00:23:20,857
He was being reckless.

280
00:23:20,983 --> 00:23:22,359
Sit back, honey.

281
00:23:23,485 --> 00:23:25,004
This isn't about making
your leg better.

282
00:23:25,028 --> 00:23:26,488
