of me. You're just unhappy.

289
00:23:43,672 --> 00:23:46,216
Unhappy people
do reckless things.

290
00:23:49,344 --> 00:23:50,929
Darrien!

291
00:23:51,013 --> 00:23:52,556
Stop screaming, my head hurts.

292
00:23:52,681 --> 00:23:54,141
