When you were screaming in my
room, what did you think you saw?

295
00:23:59,896 --> 00:24:03,358
You said, "Put it down on
the ground and get away."

296
00:24:04,318 --> 00:24:05,569
Sounds like a cop.

297
00:24:07,571 --> 00:24:08,822
Old habits, I guess.

298
00:24:09,072 --> 00:24:10,490
You were a cop?

299
