him going for his gun.

309
00:24:46,068 --> 00:24:48,528
I tried to talk him down, but...

310
00:24:55,035 --> 00:24:57,120
They told me I was a hero.

311
00:25:00,248 --> 00:25:02,417
So that's when you
started using drugs.

312
00:25:04,920 --> 00:25:06,380
I'm sorry.

313
00:25:09,925 --> 00:25:10,967
Darrien.

314
00:25:13,387 --> 00:25:15,055
Darrien!

315
00:25:15,389 --> 00:25:16,598
She lost consciousness.

316
00:25:26,441 --> 00:25:28,568
