345
00:26:50,358 --> 00:26:52,736
Give me the keys, I'll drive.

346
00:26:58,074 --> 00:26:59,409
I'll get a cab.

347
00:27:00,577 --> 00:27:02,037
Good luck with everything.

348
00:27:04,706 --> 00:27:06,875
You were defending
your friend beyond all rationality,

349
