call Ruby on mobile?

390
00:29:30,685 --> 00:29:31,853
No.

391
00:29:36,358 --> 00:29:38,818
She on any medication
besides crack?

392
00:29:38,902 --> 00:29:40,695
She was taking
interferon in prison,

393
00:29:40,820 --> 00:29:43,073
