442
00:32:12,680 --> 00:32:13,681
Yeah, it's fine.

443
00:32:16,184 --> 00:32:17,435
I'll get you some ice.

444
00:32:17,519 --> 00:32:19,229
I said it was fine.

445
00:32:21,064 --> 00:32:23,608
