would've prescribed interferon,

455
00:33:12,240 --> 00:33:14,659
unless the lab showed
her Hep-C to be chronic.

456
00:33:14,784 --> 00:33:17,453
So, what makes new
Hep-C look like old Hep-C?

457
00:33:19,414 --> 00:33:20,623
What if she got a parasite?

458
00:33:20,915 --> 00:33:22,417
The Hep-C made her susceptible,

459
00:33:22,500 --> 00:33:24,252
and the parasite sped
up the liver damage.

460
00:33:24,836 --> 00:33:26,004
Entamoeba.

461
00:33:26,087 --> 00:33:29,257
Throw in a parasitoma, the stab
wound could have freed them,

462
00:33:29,340 --> 00:33:32,969
sent them coursing through
her bloodstream, wreaking havoc.

463
00:33:33,094 --> 00:33:35,221
A single bag of metronidazole.

464
00:33:35,305 --> 00:33:38,516
If we're right, she could wake
up from the coma in a few hours.

465
00:33:51,946 --> 00:33:52,989
They're ready for you.

466
00:34:01,664 --> 00:34:02,790
Wait.

467
00:34:08,004 --> 00:34:09,297
I want you in there.

468
00:34:10,340 --> 00:34:11,549
I'm not a surgeon.

469
00:34:12,008 --> 00:34:13,509
There's nothing I can do.

470
00:34:13,635 --> 00:34:16,554
Well, you can make sure
that idiot butcher

471
00:34:16,638 --> 00:34:18,306
