473
00:34:24,020 --> 00:34:25,340
He's gonna do what
he needs to do.

474
00:34:25,396 --> 00:34:26,439
Yeah,

475
00:34:26,522 --> 00:34:29,317
and if that involves
chopping off my leg,

476
00:34:31,736 --> 00:34:35,156
I want to be sure that
that's damn well necessary.

477
00:34:37,408 --> 00:34:38,993
House...

478
00:34:39,827 --> 00:34:41,746
I don't trust him.

479
00:34:43,331 --> 00:34:45,083
I trust you.

480
00:35:21,786 --> 00:35:22,870
Can you hear me?

481
00:35:24,247 --> 00:35:25,373
Yeah.

482
00:35:27,041 --> 00:35:28,876
You had parasites in your liver.

483
00:35:29,627 --> 00:35:34,132
Probably from a dirty needle,
or prison, or who knows what.

484
00:35:34,757 --> 00:35:38,553
The stabbing made it worse,
but you're gonna be okay.

485
00:35:50,273 --> 00:35:52,900
I'm sorry. We had to.

486
00:35:57,822 --> 00:35:59,574
I told you I couldn't go back.

487
00:36:05,955 --> 00:36:07,290
I shouldn't have trusted you.

488
00:36:08,916 --> 00:36:10,418
I never liked you.

489
00:36:11,336 --> 00:36:15,423
I killed time with you 'cause
I was locked in a cage.

490
00:36:15,631 --> 00:36:18,092
You were a distraction.

491
00:36:18,426 --> 00:36:21,971
Someone to talk to so I
didn't have to think about

492
00:36:22,347 --> 00:36:23,973
